text: Running into an interesting issue with the form submission API where all submissions are shown as "direct traffic" even with the HS UTK cookie added to the payload. Anyone ever run into this?
Hey Mark, these aren’t coming from a IP range that’s set for analytics filtering is it?  That’s the most common reason for this
Hey Zack, that could be it, I'll do some testing and let you know
Zack, looks like that's not the case, my IP was not blocked. My workflow was open an incognito browser > google their site > submit form, still showed as direct.
ok, can you send me a link to that contact and the POST body if you can?
